@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to the Building Materials Platform</h1>
    <p>This platform is designed to manage building materials, their environmental characteristics, transportation factors, and more. Developed by Amani Barhoumi.</p>

    <h2>About the Project</h2>
    <p>
        The Building Materials Platform is designed to address the challenges of sustainability and responsible resource management in the construction industry.
        It provides a comprehensive database of construction materials, integrating detailed information about their physical, mechanical, and environmental characteristics.
        This platform aims to support informed decision-making, optimize costs, and promote the use of eco-friendly materials, contributing to sustainable development goals.
    </p>

    
